00001000                            33  MAPINIT
00001000                            34  ; SHOWS HARDWARE WINDOW AND GETS MAPPING ADDRESSESG.
00001000                            35  ; INPUT    - D0.B BIT 0: SHOW HARDWARE WINDOW (1: YES, 0: NO)
00001000                            36  ;                 BIT 1: GET MAPPING ADDRESSES (1: YES, 0: NO)
00001000                            37  ;                 BIT 2-7: NOT USED.
00001000                            38  ;            A0 POINTER TO RAM ADDRESS TO STORE THE MAPPING ADDRESSES IN THIS
00001000                            39  ;               ORDER: 7-SEGMENT, LEDS, SWITCHES, BUTTONS.
00001000                            40  ;               IF D0.B BIT 1 IS ZERO, A0 IS NOT USED.
00001000                            41  ; OUTPUT   - NO OUTPUT THROUGH REGISTERS
00001000                            42  ;            RAM POINTED BY A0 IS MODIFIED IF D0.B BIT 1 IS 1
00001000                            43  ; MODIFIES - NONE
00001000                            44  ; -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
