0000104A                            79  MAPPRBIT
0000104A                            80  ; PRINTS 'ZERO','ONE','TWO',...,'SEVEN' INTO THE 7-SEGMENT DISPLAYS DEPENDING
0000104A                            81  ; ON THE BUTTON THAT IS PRESSED (ZERO IS THE RIGHTMOST, SEVEN IS THE LEFTMOST).
0000104A                            82  ; PRINTS 'NONE' IF NO BUTTON IS PRESSED.
0000104A                            83  ; INPUT    - A0 BUTTONS MAPPING ADDRESS
0000104A                            84  ;            A1 7-SEGMENT DISPLAY MAPPING ADDRESS
0000104A                            85  ; OUTPUT   - NONE THROUGH REGISTERS
