00001138                           225  BITPOS
00001138                           226  ; GIVEN A BYTE, IT RETURNS THE POSITION (VALUE BETWEEN 0 AND 7) OF THE RIGHT-
00001138                           227  ; MOST BIT VALUED ONE. IF ALL BITS ARE ZERO, OUTPUTS 8
